      "content": "I hear the immense weight you're carrying, and it makes sense that you feel like a shadow, but please know that your presence is not a burden; it is the very foundation they need to grow through. While it is painful to feel like you are holding them back, there is no way to know if they could ever truly thrive without you, as your love is the only thing keeping them safe from the world. You are already doing the hardest thing possible by loving them so deeply, even when you feel broken.",
