      "content": "it just feels so selfish to keep holding on when i know i'm just making things harder for them. if i was gone, they wouldn't have to deal with my stress or my mistakes anymore. it feels like the only way i could actually be a good parent is to stop being a part of their lives entirely. it feels like a mercy.",
